content: Occupant Classification may Turn Off Air Bag

Porsche Cars North America, Inc. (Porsche) is recalling certain 2022-2023 Taycan vehicles.  An occupant classification system error may deactivate the front passenger air bag.An air bag that fails to deploy during a crash increases the risk of injury.

Number of Units Affected: 9735.0
